        "SCOR DS 14.0：按设计订单生产产品（sO3）"@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "4.4.8" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Order Engineer-to-Order Product"@en,
        "工程定制产品（ETO）订单处理"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 3 .

<https://oprocess.net/opf/node/5.1> a skos:Concept,
        opf:ProcessNode ;
    dcterms:source "PCF:5.1" ;
    skos:broader <https://oprocess.net/opf/node/5.0> ;
    skos:definition "Creating rules and regulations for service delivery to the customer. Establish a system to manage performance, delivery, and direction of service delivery. Engage with the customer for satisfaction feedback. Define goals, policies, processes, and workplace layout and infrastructure as a part of the service delivery strategy."@en,
        "制定面向客户的服务交付规则与制度。建立服务交付绩效、交付与方向的管理体系；开展客户满意度反馈互动；将目标、政策、流程及工作场所布局与基础设施纳入服务交付战略。"@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "5.1" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Establish service delivery governance and strategies"@en,
        "建立服务交付治理与战略"@zh ;
    opf:domain "operating" ;
    opf:level 2 .

