        "ITIL V5实践：关系管理（Relationship Management），对应‘构建并管理IT客户关系’。"@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
    skos:notation "8.1.8" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Relationship Management"@en,
