    skos:definition "ITIL V5 practice: Infrastructure and Platform Management. Mapped to Manage Information Technology (IT)."@en,
        "ITIL V5 实践：基础设施与平台管理。映射至「管理信息技术（IT）」。"@zh ;
    skos:inScheme <https://oprocess.net/opf> ;
